{"tid":1885113,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"火影肯定係世界第一動漫，不服來便","createTime":"2020-02-18T05:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T05:44:51.000Z","uid":272077,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fa1cbd1089aa1361562cd6a8ed6929edd43896a0","tid":1885113,"uid":272077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:22:29.000Z","msg":"人氣只係僅次於龍珠<br />\n但內容紥實好多 有意義好多<br />\n唔係淨係打打殺殺<br />\n每個奸角背後都有自己嘅故事<br />\n連實際上無出場嘅角色都好大作用 例如止水 琳<br />\n角色符合現實世界人性<br />\n天才二世祖永遠係贏家<br />\n唔似其他作品懶係野普通人打贏天才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完左5年keep住有人不斷討論<br />\n個支那仔出人物誌下下上youtube熱門<br />\n<br />\n再講分鏡完全屌打其他動漫<br />\n<br />\n伏筆勁到仆街<br />\n面具男同迪達拉捉三尾個話可以呼應返琳變三尾人柱力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲人成日屌回憶只不過係動畫組電視台問題<br />\n漫畫睇得不知集爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0b5bd7e0c0aef76c05f67156e4b24a44a6f0fd","tid":1885113,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:23:35.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"4d5bdad53dd6850dafaf7688ab45dee5c18395a9","tid":1885113,"uid":262698,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:24:13.000Z","msg":"爛尾 <br />\n人死完又翻生 不斷loop<br />\n佩恩死左之後開始失望"},{"pid":"6712fb0babcd344ffa9388d5dc72ed4517895286","tid":1885113,"uid":49057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:25:44.000Z","msg":"有無屌打其它動畫嘅分鏡例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa2b07465896224771aa0f80b9aebc1b38849fe","tid":1885113,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:25:46.000Z","msg":"Sorry<br />\n小圓先係"},{"pid":"1d7f71727a36a59fbf92e41feadcbae36a7aad0a","tid":1885113,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:29:53.000Z","msg":"鋼鍊&gt;&gt;&gt;未諗到&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;火影&gt;&